title: Anacostia Park: Plan A Field Trip
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Education     Plan A Field Trip               Plan A Field Trip       School groups are welcome! Reservations are not required for a school trip to the park, unless you would like a ranger to accompany your group. If you are interested in reserving a ranger-assisted program, call (202) 472-3873. During winter months, please call 202-426-6905. Please help us keep the park clean and plan ahead to pack out any trash, such as lunch containers.
